Please note that useful metadata may already be generated by your instruments during measurements, while working with the data have a look at the raw data files and manual to see which metadata is generated, for more information see: www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/guidance/documentation-metadata
Sharing: When depositing data in RDR a DOI will be added and you will be asked to select a license, most used is CC-BY meaning that others can use your data for any purpose but they have to acknowledge you, for more information: https://www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/rdr
